<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～<anim id="Eh" target="player" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />好難過喔～！<delay20 /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
我已經想回家了啦～！！<delay40 />
這全都是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你的錯～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對不起<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
我不是故意要讓你<delay8 />
這麼難過的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">都怪你跟我說什麼<delay8 />
《大蜘蛛與小蟑螂的悲戀》啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我的妝<anim id="Confused" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />都哭花了～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真是抱歉，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
但是<delay20 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道為什麼，<delay8 />
我要說這個故事給你聽嗎？<pageBreak />都是因為<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把注定無法和心愛之人在一起，<delay8 />
為愛所苦的女主角的身影，<delay20 /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟你重疊在一起了<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！？<delay40 />
你這樣是在誇我嗎～？<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正是說我像女主角嘛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
拜託你別說這種話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />哭泣的你，<delay8 />
簡直就像被困在陷阱中的
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />女主角一樣呢<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />被囚禁的女主角<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說<delay20 />不管我擺出什麼表情，
都會散發出女主角的氣質吧～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真是抱歉，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
但是<delay20 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道我為什麼<delay8 />
要說這個故事給你聽嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我把任性而活的你，<delay20 />
和這個故事中女主角的形象，<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />重疊在一起了<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />原來是這樣啊～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說<delay8 />我最自然的樣子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會讓人覺得是當女主角的料吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼了，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />？<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看你這麼煩惱地在嘆氣<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay20 />在音樂節目裡登場的偶像
看起來超～耀眼的！<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
看完之後我就在想<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我繼續照這個樣子練習，<delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的能夠爬到那種高度，<delay8 />
變成那麼厲害的偶像嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我未來真的有辦法……<delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成長到跟那些偶像，<delay8 />
一較高下的程度嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣太不像你了吧！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我希望你能夠保持自己<delay20 />
一直以來都充滿活力的樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你就像<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那一心一意<delay8 />
追尋著太陽的向日葵<tag a="110" b="0" />！<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是向日葵……<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
一輩子都碰不到太陽啊～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />向日葵啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯嗯，<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像花兒一樣可愛的我，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
一定可以成為頂尖偶像！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你就像夏天裡<delay8 />飛入熊熊烈火之中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不屈不撓的昆蟲一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />充滿毅力不是嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不行啦～！<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
這樣我不就變成<delay8 />一團灰燼了嗎～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是說就算是渺小的我，<delay8 />
只要有顆熱情的心還有行動力，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就一定可以變成頂尖偶像對吧！<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～既然這樣，<delay20 />
我絕～對要當上頂尖偶像，<delay8 />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓大家知道我也做得到～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺我突然又有動力了！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了成為超級厲害的頂尖偶像，<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要努力加油～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="115" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！<delay20 />很不錯喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />看來你又找回那個耀眼動人的自己了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
我也很期待<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你今後活躍的表現呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我覺得呀，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
如果把<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />打成果汁，<delay8 />
一定會超好喝的唷～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你真有趣呢。<anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然是人各有所好<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我從之前就在想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
你的口頭禪「<tag a="110" b="5" />」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像糞便之於糞金龜一樣，<delay8 />真是太棒了呢！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不介意的話，可以把那個糞……<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" />啊，不對，<delay8 />是你那太陽般閃耀的口頭禪，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也借我用用看嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼<delay20 />糞啦～！？<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
怎麼聽起來，<delay8 />
一點都不像在誇獎我～！？<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />你又說想用我的口頭禪，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那應該還是在誇我對吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我當然是在誇你啊！<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想像你的口頭禪一樣，<delay8 />
散發出耀眼的光芒<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />這絕對是真的喔！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">想跟我的口頭禪一樣<tag a="110" b="0" />？<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說屬於我的時代到了嗎！？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好唷～那你就拿去用吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「<tag a="110" b="5" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯！<delay frames="60" />
真是太適合我了，這個糞……這個口頭禪！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不客氣！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />是說<delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能不能不要再提到
糞這個字啦～？<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
